        <h2 class="main-header">About Us</h2>
        <p>We are a digital platform dedicated to improving public safety through efficient and secure crime reporting. Our system empowers individuals to report crimes quickly and anonymously, helping authorities respond more effectively. Whether it's theft, assault, vandalism, or suspicious activity, our platform provides a reliable channel for citizens to take action and contribute to a safer community.</p>
        <p>Our mission is to support law enforcement and the public by bridging the gap between crime incidents and timely reporting. We believe that everyone deserves to live in a safe environment and that access to justice starts with accessible reporting tools. Thank you for using our platform—we’re here to make a difference, one report at a time.</p>
        <p>Founded in 2021, our system has become a trusted tool for thousands of users and law enforcement agencies. Our team includes cybersecurity experts, legal advisors, and tech developers working together to maintain a system that is secure, user-friendly, and highly responsive. We are committed to upholding transparency, data privacy, and the ethical handling of all submitted reports.</p>
        <p>In addition to crime reporting, we offer informative resources such as safety tips, crime statistics, legal guidance, and community alerts. We are also working on future updates that include real-time notifications and map-based crime tracking to keep you informed and empowered. Our goal is to foster a vigilant, engaged, and informed public.</p>
        <p>We constantly seek to improve our system and better serve communities. If you have suggestions, concerns, or need assistance, we encourage you to reach out. Thank you for trusting us as your partner in crime prevention and public safety.</p>
